Possible causes for drop:-

1. Deactivation of accounts of users, a large chunk of people were relived. 
2. A large number of users busy during that time, maybe end of month work
3. Something distasteful happened on Yammer that made users to not engage on platform anymore.
4. Server down in some areas, people not able to access Yammer.
5. Holiday time
6. Code for tracking Yammer users is broken
7. Something big happened on Yammer that made the sudden spike in users' engagements. And then everything returned to normal
